snippet.title: IntelligenceIV #21 - VC 4000
snippet.description: This is a Othello clone for the Interton VC 4000. The game has many different settings to get it harder if you need, including timed play etc. This is me kicking the CPU within a few moves. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/06/intelligence-iv-21-vc-4000.html
